  "title": "Personal Assistant and Office Administrator",
  "description": "<p><strong>CONTRACT ROLE FOR 6-MONTHS (MARCH - AUGUST 2026)</strong><br /><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><p><u>Office Administrator</u></p><ul><li>   Office management – order groceries, stationery, manage cleaner, gym schedules.</li><li>Submit claims, management payments.</li><li>Handle couriers – local, international.</li><li>Manage and book travel arrangements, Visas etc.</li><li>Coordinating schedules and maintaining calendar.</li><li>Act as a liaison between management and clients/business partners.</li><li>Organize business events, meals, team-building activities.</li><li>Maintain accurate records and manage confidential information with discretion.</li><li>Provide administrative and operational support for ongoing projects and business initiatives.</li><li>Handle signing of legal/finance documents, Notary etc.</li></ul><p><u>Personal Assistant</u></p><ul><li>House management.</li><li>Personal appointments.</li><li>Personal requests – purchases, reservations, appointments, errands etc.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Job Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>Strong organizational, multitasking and time-management skills.</li><li>Excellent interpersonal and communication abilities.</li><li>Attention to detail and able to think on your feet.</li><li>Proactive, reliable and able to thrive in a dynamic environment.</li><li>Ethical and trustworthy.</li><li>Proficiency in Microsoft Office.</li><li>No prior experience required.</li><li>Able to attend to after-hours requests when necessary.</li></ul>",
